      <title>CFPB 表示，“先买后付”需要类似信用卡的监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/buy-now-pay-later-soon-will-be-treated-more-like-credit-cards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位美国金融监管机构表示，Block Inc. 旗下 Afterpay、Affirm Holdings Inc. 和 Klarna Bank AB 等“先买后付”贷款机构在某些方面应像信用卡提供商一样受到对待。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/buy-now-pay-later-soon-will-be-treated-more-like-credit-cards</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
